Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.46,0:00:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著在熱好的平底鍋上倒入油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.57,0:00:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.63,0:00:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放油時要先把鍋子\N從火上拿開才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.64,0:00:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.54,0:00:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是看煮菜節目的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.61,0:00:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳以為是因為誰的關係\N才變成這樣的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.05,0:00:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.35,0:00:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是妳，就是妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.73,0:00:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀河天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.07,0:00:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.14,0:00:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危機，這下糟糕了\N緊張！緊張！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.81,0:00:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撲克光線BURU  BURU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.75,0:00:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙大騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.11,0:00:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK，胡鬧一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.85,0:00:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒關係，吃個飲茶\N好啊！好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.62,0:01:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著歡悅的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.86,0:01:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一起向神明祈禱吧\NBANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因果報應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.56,0:01:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天都是冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.30,0:01:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.24,0:01:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓它順其自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.84,0:01:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有機關，沒有魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.31,0:01:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤注一擲的I.N.G.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.61,0:01:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無憂無慮的狂歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.15,0:01:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢想與希望的機關鎗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.05,0:01:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鎖定想要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.16,0:01:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.32,0:01:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳舞吧，玩吧，BRAVO！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.03,0:01:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐上令人興奮的火箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.70,0:01:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開闢天下無敵的成功之路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.28,0:01:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(廢校的回憶肉醬，海盜風味)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.28,0:02:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家好\N我是萊格．克萊茲曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.35,0:02:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.15,0:02:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克萊茲曼侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.66,0:02:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您想委託我們天使隊做的工作是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學生證嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.70,0:02:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.73,0:02:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本在小學畢業時就該還的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.67,0:02:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果不小心錯失歸還的機會\N而一直留在我這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.44,0:02:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把學生證還給「回憶小學」\N就可以了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.15,0:02:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以麻煩你們嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.75,0:02:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己還就行了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.48,0:02:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.18,0:02:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣就不能賺錢了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.22,0:02:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的那間小學是在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.32,0:02:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在  「謎之區」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.66,0:02:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已準備一筆相當的酬金了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是錢的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.00,0:02:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.83,0:02:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"謎之七"？\N那是很危險的地方嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是海盜的溫床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溫床？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.84,0:03:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思，克萊茲曼侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.88,0:03:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼危險的區域\N我們是不可能去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.58,0:03:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錯失歸還學生證的時機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我心裡一直覺得很遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.25,0:03:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話\N我到死都無法安心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.86,0:03:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克萊茲曼侯爵請放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這張學生證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.94,0:03:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會幫您送到\N您的母校「回憶小學」  去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.71,0:03:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.08,0:03:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.71,0:03:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡看起來好危險喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像隨時都會有東西飛過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.99,0:03:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克萊茲曼侯爵剛剛去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.06,0:03:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.73,0:03:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克萊茲曼侯爵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.43,0:03:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為委託人去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.94,0:04:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不履行任務而回基地\N也是可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.71,0:04:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼危險的地方\N我想快點離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.78,0:04:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且\N那個叔叔好像很煩惱的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳要一個人去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.95,0:04:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有蘭花在的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.39,0:04:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這台機器也不會動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.35,0:04:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且看到克萊茲曼侯爵哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.32,0:04:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然說"我也要去"的人\N可是蘭花喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.73,0:04:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？這個嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話是沒錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.30,0:04:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，沒辦法\N那就速戰速決吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.11,0:04:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...我們還是回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.41,0:04:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說這什麼話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.48,0:04:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"無論如何都要去"\N這不是妳說的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.48,0:04:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是都沒有半個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.98,0:04:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破破爛爛的好可怕耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.41,0:04:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回憶小學是在哪裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.82,0:04:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.65,0:04:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花妳不是知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.62,0:04:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我非得知道不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.16,0:04:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身心健康夢想是宇宙飛行...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.46,0:05:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.83,0:05:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回憶...回憶小學...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.24,0:05:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像隨時都會垮掉的校舍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.21,0:05:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡搞不好是海盜的隱匿處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.01,0:05:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.98,0:05:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那首校歌\N可能就是他們同伴間的暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.98,0:05:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的校歌是這間小學\N為了要引導我們來而放的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.36,0:05:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我們正在找這間小學啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.13,0:05:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳還真是個樂觀的孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小學又不是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.70,0:05:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能會做那種事嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之，既然來到這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好繼續走下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.81,0:05:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等我，蘭花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.48,0:05:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！裡面更破爛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出...出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.14,0:06:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.81,0:06:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花救命呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己也忙不過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.15,0:06:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳自己想辦法解決吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.69,0:06:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想不出辦法啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.70,0:06:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快！趁現在快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.67,0:06:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.60,0:06:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我痛得走不動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.54,0:06:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？受傷了嗎？讓我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛，只是皮肉擦傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.48,0:06:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.01,0:07:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一點小傷還可以跑啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛得跑不了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.29,0:07:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭，還有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.12,0:07:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優，妳明明還能跑嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.36,0:07:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.36,0:07:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不能再跑快點嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.13,0:07:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，被蘭花抱著跑\N輕鬆，輕鬆...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優，抓緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.25,0:07:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳幾公斤啊？\N好重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.45,0:07:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是標準體重耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.36,0:07:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別哭啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.62,0:07:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煩死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.86,0:07:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.61,0:08:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好累喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還以為死定了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.45,0:08:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，不過這樣大概會瘦一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.85,0:08:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.16,0:08:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭\N又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.07,0:08:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.30,0:08:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作點！梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.61,0:08:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會這樣子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.38,0:08:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優，不要死啊，梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不能死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.29,0:08:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.99,0:08:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了嗎？\N是我先打中敵人的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.53,0:08:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個比賽算我贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.73,0:08:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼...輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.50,0:08:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，不甘心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只差這麼一點就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.74,0:09:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.84,0:09:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是遊戲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.98,0:09:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遊戲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.05,0:09:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把進入學校的人當成目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.55,0:09:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最先打倒目標的人勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.42,0:09:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遊戲？你們說這是遊戲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.32,0:09:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，很好玩呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.82,0:09:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次再玩一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.79,0:09:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們再怎麼玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.73,0:09:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是得區分什麼可以做\N什麼不可以做呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.43,0:09:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玩遊戲竟然還殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們搞什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，那是油漆彈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.11,0:09:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？油漆彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.58,0:09:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優，妳真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.75,0:09:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我真的以為死定了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，蘭花妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些小孩沒有影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.59,0:09:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腳也是透明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.76,0:10:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們該不會是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.13,0:10:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克萊茲曼先生的學生證...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克萊茲曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回來啦，萊格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.46,0:10:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好慢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.66,0:10:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於可以一起玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩位姊姊，謝謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.58,0:10:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個...莫非是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.55,0:11:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幽靈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，小孩的幽靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可能是集體幻覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.96,0:11:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優和蘭花\N看到了相同的幻覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.43,0:11:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.80,0:11:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花，剛才明明看到...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務完成，準備返回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.37,0:11:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.17,0:11:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花，為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.18,0:11:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣不是很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.71,0:11:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克萊茲曼侯爵的學生證\N也平安回到了小學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就夠了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.55,0:11:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔，說得也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.92,0:11:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是小時候快樂的心\N還留在學校裡玩耍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.63,0:11:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(下個菜單是\N佛特的遺跡燉煮麻煩醬菜)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.23,0:11:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是很可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裡可愛了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.60,0:11:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，要不要抱抱看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.87,0:11:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.61,0:11:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不要客氣沒關係呀，請吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.54,0:11:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是跟妳說過我不要嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳怎麼流這麼多汗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.63,0:12:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滿天的星辰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.37,0:12:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是打翻水瓶似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.61,0:12:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我新月的曲線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.68,0:12:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做了夢之後，變得想見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.25,0:12:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,側耳傾聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.35,0:12:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，不是聽見了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.26,0:12:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人興奮的天線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.10,0:12:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要讓它睡著  NO  NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.34,0:13:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,處女座的我
